Hi there! How can I assist you today with NewsBreak? If you have any questions or need help, feel free to ask!
I can't seem to navigate the platform? Can I get help. Ive used it before so not sure what has changed?

I'm here to help! Could you let me know which specific area of the platform you're having trouble with? For example, is it related to account login, ad management, or something else? Once I have more details, I can guide you through the process.
I want to start an ad

No worries, let's tackle this step by step! If you're having trouble with account management, you can check out our Account Management Guide for detailed instructions on navigating your account. Here's the link: [Account Management Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17539290349709-Account-Management-Guide). If you need help with creating or managing ad accounts, this article might be useful: [How to create separate ad accounts](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/20333724725133-How-to-create-separate-ad-accounts). Let me know if there's a specific area you'd like more help with!
